## Limitations

The findings in this report are based on available literature and may not encompass all perspectives on the causes of domestic abuse. The complexity of human behavior and the influence of diverse cultural and societal factors mean that individual cases of domestic abuse can vary significantly. Additionally, the report relies on secondary sources, which may have inherent biases or limitations in their scope of research. Further empirical studies are needed to deepen the understanding of domestic abuse dynamics.